      <title>
        <![CDATA[ You Can Wander Through A Gigantic Field Of 700,000 Sunflowers Near Toronto ]]>
      </title>
      <link>https://www.narcity.com/toronto/you-can-visit-a-sunflower-field-near-toronto-with-700000-blooms</link>
      <content:encoded>
        <![CDATA[ <p>You can find a dreamy <a href="https://www.narcity.com/toronto/torontos-the-sunflower-farm-is-opening-this-week-its-stunning-photos" target="_blank">sunflower field near Toronto</a> this summer, and it makes a fantastic weekend adventure.</p><p>Just 40 minutes outside of the city, <a href="https://www.narcity.com/toronto/campbells-cross-farm-dinner-lets-you-eat-with-your-friends-in-a-sunflower-field" target="_blank">Campbell&apos;s Cross Farm</a> is a 60-acre garden you&apos;ll want to see for yourself.<br></p><div class="rm-shortcode" data-rm-shortcode-id="de8da1d136e7080e738a3e50547e86a0" id="47a4d"><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/CEGSTN2H7Z6/" data-instgrm-version="4" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"> <div style="padding:8px;"> <div style=" background:#F8F8F8; line-height:0; margin-top:40px; padding:50% 0; text-align:center; width:100%;"> <div style=" background:url(data:image/png;base64,); display:block; height:44px; margin:0 auto -44px; position:relative; top:-22px; width:44px;"> </div></div><p style=" margin:8px 0 0 0; padding:0 4px;"> <a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/CEGSTN2H7Z6/" style=" color:#000; font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:14px; font-style:normal; font-weight:normal; line-height:17px; text-decoration:none; word-wrap:break-word;" target="_top"></a></p> </div></blockquote></div><p>While here, you&apos;ll be able to explore the <a href="https://www.narcity.com/ontario-flower-places-are-like-being-lost-in-a-painting" target="_blank">floral paradise</a> by following the one-way pathways through the field of 700,000 golden sunflowers.</p><p>Then you can visit the adorable watermelon hut that sells refreshing watermelon sandwiches, perfect for helping you cool down on a hot day.</p><p>This year, the flowers are expected to be ready at the start of August and last up to four weeks, giving you plenty of time to visit.<br></p> <div class="rebellt-item col1" data-basename="campbells-cross-farm" data-href="https://www.narcity.com/toronto/you-can-visit-a-sunflower-field-near-toronto-with-700000-blooms/campbells-cross-farm" data-id="2" data-is-image="False" data-post-id="2653277162" data-published-at="1623158623" data-reload-ads="false" data-use-pagination="False" id="rebelltitem2"> <h3 data-role="headline"> Campbell&#x2019;s Cross Farm </h3> <div class="rm-shortcode" data-rm-shortcode-id="7d45d3869bf95cba258a4a3ba216e20b" id="c5fba"><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/B1jvwZqgMyv/" data-instgrm-version="4" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"> <div style="padding:8px;"> <div style=" background:#F8F8F8; line-height:0; margin-top:40px; padding:50% 0; text-align:center; width:100%;"> <div style=" background:url(data:image/png;base64,); display:block; height:44px; margin:0 auto -44px; position:relative; top:-22px; width:44px;"> </div></div><p style=" margin:8px 0 0 0; padding:0 4px;"> <a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/B1jvwZqgMyv/" style=" color:#000; font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:14px; font-style:normal; font-weight:normal; line-height:17px; text-decoration:none; word-wrap:break-word;" target="_top"></a></p> </div></blockquote></div> <p>Price: $13.50 per person</p><p>When: August (exact dates TBA)</p><p>Address: 3634 King St., Caledon, ON</p><p><span></span>Why You Need To Go: In addition to the yummy sandwiches, they also have watermelon lemonade and gelato.</p><p><a href="https://www.campbellscrossfarm.com/" target="_blank">Website</a></p> </div><p></p><div class="lml-template" data-id="5ef2765b1c64664ce0c3c9fc" data-type="template"> <div class="liliumtempl"><hr> <p><em data-stringify-type="italic">Before you get going, check our <a href="https://www.narcity.com/responsible-travel-guidelines">Responsible Travel Guide</a> so you can be informed, be safe, be smart, and most of all, be respectful on your adventure.</em></p> <hr> <p>&#xA0;</p> </div> </div><p></p><div class="post-pager js-listicle-pager" data-listicle-style data-async_load_parameters="platform=desktop&amp;display_ads=1&amp;settings=%7B%22enter_url%22%3A+null%2C+%22no_post_section%22%3A+null%2C+%22ads_breaks%22%3A+null%2C+%22prevent_last_break_repetition%22%3A+false%2C+%22use_numeration%22%3A+false%2C+%22show_columns_on_mobile%22%3A+null%2C+%22ads_order%22%3A+%5B2%5D%2C+%22turn_into_posts%22%3A+null%2C+%22list_breaks%22%3A+null%2C+%22reorder_voting%22%3A+null%2C+%22cooldown_in_seconds%22%3A+null%2C+%22pagination_order%22%3A+null%2C+%22source%22%3A+%22engine_settings%22%2C+%22next_post_url%22%3A+null%2C+%22up_down_voting%22%3A+false%2C+%22allow_url_change%22%3A+null%2C+%22numeration_sort%22%3A+-1%2C+%22allow_url_update%22%3A+null%2C+%22use_pagination%22%3A+false%2C+%22body_text_above%22%3A+false%2C+%22use_ads%22%3A+false%2C+%22items_as_posts%22%3A+false%2C+%22multiple_answers%22%3A+null%2C+%22no_redirect%22%3A+null%2C+%22is_guest_voting_allowed%22%3A+null%2C+%22layout_type%22%3A+null%2C+%22voting_extra_fields%22%3A+null%7D"> </div><div class="around-the-web"><div class="from-your-site__headline">From Your Site Articles</div> <ul class="around-the-web__list"><li class="from-your-site__item"> <a href="https://www.narcity.com/toronto/campbells-cross-farm-dinner-lets-you-eat-with-your-friends-in-a-sunflower-field" class="from-your-site__link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Campbell&apos;s Cross Farm Dinner Lets You Eat With Your Friends In A ... &#x203A;</a> </li><li class="from-your-site__item"> <a href="https://www.narcity.com/