      <guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.narcity.com/toronto/lavelle-is-reopening-its-toronto-rooftop-patio-with-boozy-treats</guid>
      <title>
        <![CDATA[ This Towering Poolside Patio Is Reopening In Toronto With Boozy Bubble Tea &amp; More ]]>
      </title>
      <link>https://www.narcity.com/toronto/lavelle-is-reopening-its-toronto-rooftop-patio-with-boozy-treats</link>
      <content:encoded>
        <![CDATA[ <p>One of Toronto&apos;s <a href="https://www.narcity.com/toronto/15-rooftop-patios-in-toronto-that-are-seriously-perfect-on-a-sunny-day" target="_blank">popular rooftop patios</a> is gearing up to welcome guests back, and it&apos;s got some exciting new things in store.</p><p>Lavelle, a restaurant and bar located 16 stories above the city, is reopening on June 11, and you can expect to see new food items, decor, and more.</p><div class="rm-shortcode" data-rm-shortcode-id="fdab1efe209f527bc0813ac0c1679aab" id="83110"><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/CCrZzcDpx8u/" data-instgrm-version="4" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"> <div style="padding:8px;"> <div style=" background:#F8F8F8; line-height:0; margin-top:40px; padding:50% 0; text-align:center; width:100%;"> <div style=" background:url(data:image/png;base64,); display:block; height:44px; margin:0 auto -44px; position:relative; top:-22px; width:44px;"> </div></div><p style=" margin:8px 0 0 0; padding:0 4px;"> <a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/CCrZzcDpx8u/" style=" color:#000; font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:14px; font-style:normal; font-weight:normal; line-height:17px; text-decoration:none; word-wrap:break-word;" target="_top"></a></p> </div></blockquote></div><p><strong>The venue will be serving some unique treats to keep you cool, such as bubble tea, frappucinos, and hibiscus snow cones, all of which are available with a <a href="https://www.narcity.com/toronto/torontos-giant-cocktails-are-so-massive-you-only-need-one-to-get-turnt" target="_blank">boozy twist</a>.</strong><br></p><p class="shortcode-media shortcode-media-rebelmouse-image"> <img class="rm-shortcode rm-lazyloadable-image" data-rm-shortcode-id="0e9411f93536e17bc3e4a8b6624a1fd9" data-rm-shortcode-name="rebelmouse-image" data-runner-src="https://www.narcity.com/media-library/eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJpbWFnZSI6Imh0dHBzOi8vYXNzZXRzLnJibC5tcy8yNjU5Nzc0Mi9vcmlnaW4uanBnIiwiZXhwaXJlc19hdCI6MTY2MzYzNzE1NX0.WQZ2EWgtGGqTfzQMCkI2IyHOpSCBkw_lv_H45wIf6AI/image.jpg?width=980" height="3024" id="f4d4c" lazy-loadable="true" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg xmlns=&apos;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&apos; viewBox=&apos;0 0 4032 3024&apos;%3E%3C/svg%3E" width="4032"> <small class="image-media media-photo-credit" placeholder="Add Photo Credit..."><a href="https://chezlavelle.com" target="_blank">Lavelle | Handout</a></small></p><p><strong>The seating areas have been updated with more umbrellas, chandelier-filled cabanas, and even swinging basket chairs that boast views of the <a href="https://www.narcity.com/toronto/11-spots-to-seek-some-spectacular-sunsets-near-toronto" target="_blank">sunset</a> and CN Tower.</strong></p><p class="shortcode-media shortcode-media-rebelmouse-image"> <img class="rm-shortcode rm-lazyloadable-image" data-rm-shortcode-id="3fe7ee0796a2375a2350f182254ce3d9" data-rm-shortcode-name="rebelmouse-image" data-runner-src="https://www.narcity.com/media-library/eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJpbWFnZSI6Imh0dHBzOi8vYXNzZXRzLnJibC5tcy8yNjU5Nzc0Ny9vcmlnaW4uanBnIiwiZXhwaXJlc19hdCI6MTY0ODcwNjQ4M30.KEt3TMkbcgHr9FheV8dW5YsQuljKBFUHu9Aij306P2Y/image.jpg?width=980" height="3024" id="cdcda" lazy-loadable="true" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg xmlns=&apos;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&apos; viewBox=&apos;0 0 4032 3024&apos;%3E%3C/svg%3E" width="4032"> <small class="image-media media-photo-credit" placeholder="Add Photo Credit..."><a href="https://chezlavelle.com" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">Lavelle | Handout</a></small></p><p><strong>Loaded hot dogs, giant seafood towers, boozy popsicles, sushi rolls, and mocktails are some of the things you can expect to find on the menu this season.</strong></p><p class="shortcode-media shortcode-media-rebelmouse-image"> <img class="rm-shortcode rm-lazyloadable-image" data-rm-shortcode-id="428291a9781c257b2dfd37667bfd1008" data-rm-shortcode-name="rebelmouse-image" data-runner-src="https://www.narcity.com/media-library/eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJpbWFnZSI6Imh0dHBzOi8vYXNzZXRzLnJibC5tcy8yNjU5Nzc1NC9vcmlnaW4uanBnIiwiZXhwaXJlc19hdCI6MTY1NzA0NDkzNH0.7GrAFPPwTet_lsB4J_0p6piNn5UROrA38ICxJStQMPU/image.jpg?width=980" height="2715" id="851d5" lazy-loadable="true" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg xmlns=&apos;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&apos; viewBox=&apos;0 0 4088 2715&apos;%3E%3C/svg%3E" width="4088"> <small class="image-media media-photo-credit" placeholder="Add Photo Credit..."><a href="https://chezlavelle.com" target="_blank">Michelle Casselman | Lavelle</a></small></p><p><strong>Similar to last year, the venue will have 3 pools available with distancing regulations, safety protocols, and a DJ from Wednesday to Sunday.</strong></p><div class="rm-shortcode" data-rm-shortcode-id="48e2b30252f56b2190524d344ccbcb75" id="b85fc"><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/CDNEaROgDpB/" data-instgrm-version="4" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"> <div style="padding:8px;"> <div style=" background:#F8F8F8; line-height:0; margin-top:40px; padding:50% 0; text-align:center; width:100%;"> <div style=" background:url(data:image/png;base64,); display:block; height:44px; margin:0 auto -44px; position:relative; top:-22px; width:44px;"> </div></div><p style=" margin:8px 0 0 0; padding:0 4px;"> <a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/CDNEaROgDpB/" style=" color:#000; font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:14px; font-style:normal; font-weight:normal; line-height:17px; text-decoration:none; word-wrap:break-word;" target="_top"></a></p> </div></blockquote></div><p><strong>The restaurant is already <a href="https://www.narcity.com/toronto/toronto-patio-reservations-are-already-available-at-these-spots" target="_blank">accepting reservations</a>, so get ready for warm-weather treats and sweeping city views on this rooftop patio.</strong><br></p> <div class="rebellt-item col1" data-basename="lavelle" data-href="https://www.narcity.com/toronto/lavelle-is-reopening-its-toronto-rooftop-patio-with-boozy-treats/lavelle" data-id="2" data-is-image="True" data-post-id="2653282144" data-published-at="1623187090" data-reload-ads="false" data-use-pagination="False" id="rebelltitem2"> <h3 data-role="headline"> Lavelle </h3> <img class="rm-shortcode rm-lazyloadable-image" data-rm-shortcode-id="6509403c15f189119ec6292b25d2db30" data-rm-shortcode-name="rebelmouse-image" data-runner-src="https://www.narcity.com/media-library/eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJpbWFnZSI6Imh0dHBzOi8vYXNzZXRzLnJibC5tcy8yNjU5Nzc4My9vcmlnaW4uanBnIiwiZXhwaXJlc19hdCI6MTY4MTcyMTkxMX0.mR5YdKpZJlAnR1s26SD8RVlI_lFgB3mACPZ58NcfrDw/image.jpg?width=980" height="4032" id="3b6d5" lazy-loadable="true" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg xmlns=&apos;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&apos; viewBox=&apos;0 0 3024 4032&apos;%3E%3C/svg%3E" width="3024"> <small class="image-media media-photo-credit"><p><a href="https://chezlavelle.com" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">Lavelle | Handout</a></p></small> <p>Price: &#x1F4B8;&#x1F4B8;&#x1F4B8;</p><p>Cuisine: Japanese-Brazilian</p><p>Address: 627 King St. W., Toronto, ON</p><p>Why You Need To Go: Cool off with boozy snow cones and enjoy the view from the new swinging basket chairs at this popular summer spot.</p><p><a href="https://chezlavelle.com/menu/" target="_blank">Menu</a><br></p> </div><p><strong><br></strong></p><div class="post-pager js-listicle-pager" data-listicle-style data-async_load_parameters="platform=desktop&amp;display_ads=1&amp;settings=%7B%22enter_url%22%3A+null%2C+%22no_post_section%22%3A+null%2C+%22ads_breaks%22%3A+null%2C+%22prevent_last_break_repetition%22%3A+false%2C+%22use_numeration%22%3A+false%2C+%22show_columns_on_mobile%22%3A+null%2C+%22ads_order%22%3A+%5B2%5D%2C+%22turn_into_posts%22%3A+null%2C+%22list_breaks%22%3A+null%2C+%22reorder_voting%22%3A+null%2C+%22cooldown_in_seconds%22%3A+null%2C+%22pagination_order%22%3A+null%2C+%22source%22%3A+%22engine_settings%22%2C+%22next_post_url%22%3A+null%2C+%22up_down_voting%22%3A+false%2C+%22allow_url_change%22%3A+null%2C+%22numeration_sort%22%3A+-1%2C+%22allow_url_update%22%3A+null%2C+%22use_pagination%22%3A+false%2C+%22body_text_above%22%3A+false%2C+%22use_ads%22%3A+false%2C+%22items_as_posts%22%3A+false%2C+%22multiple_answers%22%3A+null%2C+%22no_redirect%22%3A+null%2C+%22is_guest_voting_allowed%22%3A+null%2C+%22layout_type%22%3A+null%2C+%22voting_extra_fields%22%3A+null%7D"> </div><div class="around-the-web"><div class="from-your-site__headline">From Your Site Articles</div> <ul class="around-the-web__list"><li class="from-your-site__item"> <a href="https://www.narcity.com/toronto/toronto-outdoor-swimming-pools-that-are-the-perfect-summer-oasis" class="from-your-site__link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Toronto Outdoor Swimming Pools That Are The Perfect Summer ... &#x203A;</a> </li><li class="from-your-site__item"> <a href="https://www.narcity.com/torontos-rooftop-patios-bring-you-views-of-the-entire-city" class="from-your-site__link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Toronto&apos;s Rooftop Patios Bring You Views Of The Entire City - Narcity &#x203A;</a> </li></ul></div> ]]>
